Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么有去七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里有条像样的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目那家伙  都叫他跟紧点了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是给我走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就等他5秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丑猫是…  记得是夏目家的猫猫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫猫老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很羞人的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你胖太算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫咪老师  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你是那个什么田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个傻瓜还挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  你还没从夏目那里听说我的真实身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪啊  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总体来说确实是的  不过我可是非常高贵的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我当成路边的那种小妖混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次能和妖怪交谈  这还是我的头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  你并不是能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以夏目才没把我的事告诉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你也帮不上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏目的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目是我收的小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有给夏目带来困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是你比较像小弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是你威胁了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  随便你说话就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须要隐匿证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就开动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫为什么会和你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师就像是我的保镖一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  不想说的话也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为情况比较复杂  我也不知道该怎么说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…并不是想瞒着田沼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是想瞒着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想和田沼你能正常的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想让你有不好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不好的回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看吧  我抓到大鱼了  看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是祭典  今晚会举行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  秋季庙会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去看看吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没准备完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在准备也没关系  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等啦  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的话回去正好顺路  我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  还没好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都说了还在准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为至少会有路边摊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  还没开始呢  有你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为受人之托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧…在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有？ 你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻嘛  我听说这种热闹的地方最容易聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛  确实  有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯  抱歉  帮我把这些搬到前殿那去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  帮忙把那些搬到前殿去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家拜托的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别顶撞班长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一个班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你别去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人等一下就会帮你拿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下  我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的话  夏目一定也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天居然就是狐狸的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  竟然敢捣乱  你这小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是看不到我们的样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我都快准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋  不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  救救我  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太粗暴了点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你没关系吧  给我闪边去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到这狐狸弄翻的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里只有它在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是风大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙看得到我们啊  怪物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  麦茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是空无一物到令人吃惊的地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天花板的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是池塘反射上去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭院里根本没有池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得可能天花板上的水纹只有我们才能看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼他看不到池塘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  被他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目家的丑猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子在我这的话  夏目就一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  有没有绳子  呀  越牢越好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  夏目  那不是胡子  是肩胛骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得懂我的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识夏目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  夏目也听得懂我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来见那个人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  能见到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么谢谢你了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}  跟着它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能镇静点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志他要直接去参加祭典的话告诉我们不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  万一遇到事故的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是爱担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了那种事  猫五郎会回来告诉我们的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开玩笑啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志来我们家有多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是一直以来留下了太多不好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么随便一点我也会轻松些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此之间都那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不像一家人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得还是早了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  别人掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人掉落的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  先放在我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这个好像是别人掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  被抓住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  民子来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢  胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胖太？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我自言自语而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了  就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到呢  钱袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起在哪里掉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有那么重要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那边也找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你果然也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  猫咪老…不  有没有看到我家的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只胖猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  我的回转烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  我刚才不是给你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没拿到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没拿到怎么付你钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请问要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面到底放了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我在一段时间内变成人类样子的药
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是兽型的话  会给夏目添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么就由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被食物的香味引诱来的吗  小狐狸  不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它跑进来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我把它拿到山上放生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的锅煮沸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  我明明开的小火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子跑来人群里可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  可是  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}  你在的话也就是说  名取先生他也在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  他和人有约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人拜托你跟着这孩子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫无戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有人烟的地方和我这样的存在交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会被人忌讳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我是能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个烂好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…难道是刚才的小狐狸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位哥哥是好人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过夏目那家伙  居然都不来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  丑猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近确实有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  不过很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  夏目你是不是看到庭院里的池塘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我只能看到天花板上的倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐知道吗  你能看到这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们很温柔\N我觉得我说出来的话  他们一定会接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也因为他们很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会想到我一直以来的遭遇  为我心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样想可能很自私  我不想他们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们可以一直微笑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  比想象中还要棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为乡下的话会更挫一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  其实我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个巨大的家伙挡住我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的家伙  妖怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但我能感觉到很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它都看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走一段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许有夏目你也能看清楚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话可以看得清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些倒影里的鱼  其实是什么颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊  忘恩负义的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着重要的保镖不管  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的脚步声渐渐接近的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:22:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这里却很温暖
